                                <h5>How much does carsharing cost?</h5>
                                <img class="icon-small" id="arrow-down-4" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-down-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                                <img class="icon-small d-none" id="arrow-up-4" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-up-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse multi-collapse" id="answer-4">
                                <div class="text-secondary">
                                    We have different tariffs based on the class of the car you select and on the trip length. The minimum cost is $ 1 per minute.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul class="col-6 list-group list-group-flush">
                        <li class="list-group-item" id="question-list-5" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#answer-5"  role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="answer-5">
                            <div class="d-flex justify-content-between">
                                <h5>What if I need extra time? </h5>
                                <img class="icon-small" id="arrow-down-5" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-down-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                                <img class="icon-small d-none" id="arrow-up-5" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-up-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse multi-collapse" id="answer-5">
                                <div class="text-secondary">
                                    When booking a car, you specify the duration of your rental. If you need some extra time, a special tariff will be applied.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </li>
