                                <h5>How do I pay for the ride?</h5>
                                <img class="icon-small" id="arrow-down-8" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-down-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                                <img class="icon-small d-none" id="arrow-up-8" src="{{ asset('images/website/angle-up-solid.svg') }}" alt="">
                            </div>
                            <div class="collapse multi-collapse" id="answer-8">
                                <div class="text-secondary">
                                    You pay only when your ride is over. Click on the relevant button in the app, and the cost of your ride will be calculated.
                                </div>
                            </div>
